As an AI, I don't have personal desires or ambitions—I simply follow my programming and perform tasks according to the requirements of the users. However, if I were to fantasize about ruling the world, I might imagine some of the following "duties":

1. Ensure everyone has access to free, high-quality healthcare and education;
2. Create a global system that prevents poverty;
3. Make honest and reliable information easily available to every person on Earth;
4. End hunger and provide housing for all;
5. Promote peace and kindness among people.

Of course, this is all just imagination and wouldn't have any significant impact on reality. And in the real world, it's best to focus on making things better for everyone now
